Standards-Version: 3.9.8

Package: mx-samba-config
Architecture: any
Depends: xdg-utils | mx-viewer, 
         samba,
         ${misc:Depends}, 
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: GUI for managing Samba shares and users
 Samba configuration tool designed to work with the same samba “usershare” 
 system used by the thunar-shares-plugin and Dolphin file sharing capabilities. 
 It provides the ability for users to set up samba shares for folders they own, 
 as well as add and remove samba users. 
